    "# Quick-look pipeline\n",
    "\n",
    "In-the-field reduction of the FITS files written by `hline_observer.py`. Goal: load the files, flag RFI per integration, stack across time, subtract a baseline, and look for a bump near the 21 cm line at 1420.4 MHz.\n",
    "\n",
    "Fill in the `TODO`s as you go. Keep the inline plots between steps; they are how you tell whether each stage is doing what it should."
    "\n",
    "You can use the data inn the data_2026_05_07 folder to test your code"
    "\n",
   ]
  },
